headline: CBRE Deepens AI And Data Center Push As Valuation Gap Persists
summary: CBRE Group (NYSE:CBRE) is expanding its focus on artificial intelligence and data center services as commercial real estate undergoes technology driven disruption. Executives recently highlighted the company’s AI and data center priorities, including the Pearce Services acquisition, as a key part of its service mix.
